headline: ICE First Look at Mortgage Performance: Mortgage Delinquencies Continue to Slowly Rise with FHA Performance in the Spotlight
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK, March 21, 2025--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE:ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, reports the following "first look" at February 2025 month-end mortgage performance statistics derived from its loan-level database representing the majority of the national mortgage market.
